    <element name="The Crooked Moon 2014" type="Source" source="Core" id="ID_LOA_THE_CROOKED_MOON_2014">
        <description>
            <p>You are about to embark upon a journey into the unknown, where uncanny folk with strange superstitions revere the Old Ways, and creatures of folklore lurk on the isolated fringes of civilization. The Crooked Moon is a tome intended to equip you with all the tools you’ll need to bring Folk Horror to 5E and turn your game into a terrifying tale told among friends.</p>
